\[
\sum_{k=0}^{n-1} C_k^{m+k} = \sum_{k=0}^{n-1} \binom{n}{k} \cdot (n(k+1))^{m+k}
\]

Substitute \( n \):
\[
\sum_{k=0}^{n-1} C_k^{m+k} = \sum_{k=0}^{n-1} \binom{n}{k} \cdot (n(k+1))^m
\]

