is a common difference of the arithmetic sequence defined by:

\[a_1 a_2 a_3 \cdots a_n, b_1 a_2 a_3 \cdots a_n, b_1 b_2 a_3 \cdots a_n, \ldots, b_1 b_2 b_3 \cdots b_n\]

